    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="multiple-places-230311-dusk"><a href="#multiple-places-230311-dusk" class="headerlink" title="multiple places_230311_dusk"></a>multiple places_230311_dusk</h2><p>Urocissa erythrorhyncha  喜鹊  Magpie | Turdus hortulorum灰背鸫Grey-backed Thrush | Pica Pica喜鹊Common Magpie | Pycnonotus sinensis白头鹎Chinese Bulbul | Tarsiger cyanurus红胁蓝尾鸲Red-flanked Bush Robin | Garrulax perspicillatus黑脸噪鹛Spectacled Laughingthrush | Passer montanus麻雀Tree Sparrow | Aegithalos caudatus银喉长尾山雀Long-tailed Tit | Vanellus cinereus灰头麦鸡Grey-headed Lapwing | Gallinula chloropus黑水鸡Common Moorhen</p><hr><h1 id="Scene-1-Waiting"><a href="#Scene-1-Waiting" class="headerlink" title="Scene 1:Waiting"></a>Scene 1:Waiting</h1><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/vFmZX6i1BQz9PKe.jpg" alt="wait in line"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/Li78jAJo54MHWdq.jpg" alt="Astonishing blue reveals the truth that it has managed hard life over 2 years, which is rare for a robin tiny "></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/cVmSR7FTZX6jyKJ.jpg" alt="Unlike its familiar cousin, grey-backed thrush is much more timid. "></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/ftUKpG9icOSJDMx.jpg" alt="take this veil, from off my eyes"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/guKbh6J8WryOM4C.jpg" alt="stay, and together"></p><hr><h1 id="Scene-2-Searching"><a href="#Scene-2-Searching" class="headerlink" title="Scene 2:Searching"></a>Scene 2:Searching</h1><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/uiY7mjpIwfoZkRc.jpg" alt="almost like stumbling in the flower field"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/7XcuJBVjia2DRkq.jpg" alt="drinking, meditating, or haunting?"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/TzEBin4YW5ksOfJ.jpg" alt="heart-shaped wing"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/s6KlD7d3EnFTJOM.jpg" alt="distant calling"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/mEhBcdnUbe9tJTf.jpg" alt="too hard to focus"></p><hr><h1 id="Scene-3-Review"><a href="#Scene-3-Review" class="headerlink" title="Scene 3:Review"></a>Scene 3:Review</h1><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/rmD9bEAXiwHalQ6.jpg" alt="petals feast"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/O1bNaWK5fT2L7jI.jpg" alt="noisy, noisy"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/04/17/sdklXqTLa315nQm.jpg" alt="April is the golden month to adore a tiny robin or two"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
